          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#1e293b' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='10'>Revenue momentum is uneven — 5 months saw net churn outpace growth</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#94a3b8' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='9'>Monthly net MRR change · indigo = net positive · red = net negative · Aug 2024 worst month at -$35,567</run>
